title: Lily Rabe talks AHS: Double Feature | New Interview!
author: AHS Crave
comment: I hope that when she said "the world is completely different" I hope she didn't mean that this season will take place in an alternate universe, since AHS should just stick to its one and only amazing universe in which all the other seasons also take place.
description:
